&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS or MS in Computer Science or other technical degree.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years relevant technical experience with AI systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years relevant software engineering work experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience leading large software and science teams including senior ICs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building and deploying large-scale machine learning systems with feedback loops for continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable leading full-stack / backend development in addition to science and research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An ideal candidate also has:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
