&lt;li&gt;Proven track record for innovation and delivering value to customers using AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer orientation and intensive focus on improving the customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building, deploying, and optimizing AI systems than span edge devices and the cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building products and solutions that rely on CV or sensor fusion.&lt;/li&gt;
